    ns1:inpersonHours "33 horas (42.3%)"@es ;
    ns1:numberOfCredits 3.0 ;
    ns1:otherInformation """The course will be taught in English.
Besides the use of the Moodle platform, in case of need, the communication between professors and students will be carried out using Zoom.
The answers of the tests questions will not be published since each student answers different ones, randomly drawn from a pool of questions.
The use of AI tools is prohibited and may lead to a disciplinary action. In that sense, any evaluation or submission is open to require a supplementary oral assessment by the teacher to validate that it has been made by the student without the help of AI systems.

Relationship with Sustainable Development Goals:
On the one hand, the course contributes to SDG 4 (sub-objetive 4.4): Increase the number of young and adult people having professional and technical competences necessary to have access to employment and entrepreneurship.
On the other hand, the course studies fundamental mathematical and statistical tools to be employed in the modelling of different types of systems such as biological ones (SDG 3), data processing ones for industrial innovation and sustainable cities/communities (SDGs 9 and 11), climate ones (SDG 13) or ecosystems (SDGs 14 and 15)."""@es ;
    ns1:periodEndingMonth "Enero"@es ;
    ns1:periodStartingMonth "Septiembre"@es ;
    ns1:teachingPeriod "2025-26" ;
    ns1:teachingPeriodMonths "Septiembre-Enero"@es ;
    ns1:totalHours "33 horas"@es ;
    schema:activitiesWorkload "100%"@es ;
    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000939/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description """The primary part of the course covers the fundamental aspects of frequentist statistical inference (parameter estimation, hypothesis tests, linear regression), and their application to solve engineering problems.
In addition, the Montecarlo and Bootstrap techniques, together with some fundamental aspects of Bayesian inference are also addressed.
Finally, some links among fundamentals of statistical inference, principal elements of causal inference and some basic machine learning paradigms are also outlined."""@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/pedro.zufiria%40upm.es> ;
    schema:inLanguage "Inglés"@es ;
    schema:instructor <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/pedro.zufiria%40upm.es> ;
    schema:name "Análisis Estadístico"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000939/2025-26/CB06> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CB06" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Poseer y comprender conocimientos que aporten una base u oportunidad de ser originales en el desarrollo y/o aplicación de ideas, a menudo en un contexto de investigación/ Students have demonstrated knowledge and understanding providing the groundwork or opportunity for innovation in developing and/or applying ideas, often within a research context"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000939/2025-26/CB07> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CB07" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Que los estudiantes sepan aplicar los conocimientos adquiridos y su capacidad de resolución de problemas en entornos nuevos o poco conocidos dentro de contextos más amplios (o multidisciplinares) relacionados con su área de estudio/ Students are capable of applying their knowledge, understanding, and problem"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000939/2025-26/CB10> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CB10" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Que los estudiantes posean las habilidades de aprendizaje que les permitan continuar estudiando de un modo que habrá de ser en gran medida autodirigido o autónomo/ Students have the learning skills that they require to pursue their studies in a largely self"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000939/2025-26/CT01> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CT01" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Capacidad para comprender los contenidos de clases magistrales, conferencias y seminarios en lengua inglesa/ Students are capable of understanding the content of lectures, conferences, and seminars in English"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000939/2025-26/CT04> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CT04" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Capacidad para trabajar de forma efectiva como individuo, organizando y planificando su propio trabajo, de forma independiente o como miembro de un equipo/ Students are capable of working effectively on an individual basis, organizing and planning one's own workload, either independently or as part of a team"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000939/2025-26/CT05> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CT05" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Capacidad para gestionar la información, identificando las fuentes necesarias, los principales tipos de documentos técnicos y científicos, de una manera adecuada y eficiente/ Students are capable of managing information, identifying the required sources and the main types of scientific and technical documents"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000939/2025-26/CT06> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CT06" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Capacidad para emitir juicios sobre implicaciones económicas, administrativas, sociales, éticas y medioambientales ligadas a la aplicación de sus conocimientos/ Students are capable of providing judgments on the economic, administrative, social, ethical, and environmental implications linked to the application of their knowledge"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000939/2025-26/RA12> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA12" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Capability to construct probabilistic models from experimental data using inference tools."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000939/2025-26/RA13> a ns1:LearningResult ;
